{"tid":1803401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"城門水塘現男子浮屍","createTime":"2019-12-30T07:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T15:34:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0e96185d89cc6f35d1578bffbad35bbb953c0ead","tid":1803401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T07:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20191230/s00001/54af77aa96eaf3ac1f74626335d363c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20191230%2Fs00001%2F54af77aa96eaf3ac1f74626335d363c5.jpg&h=367d8eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早上近11時，有政府人員發現一名男子於荃灣城門水塘近主壩離岸約2米水塘載浮載沉，消防趕至派出蛙人將男子撈起，救護員當場證實男子不治。警方正調查死者身分及事件原因。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線<br />\n生命熱線：2382 0000<br />\n撒瑪利亞防止自殺會：2389 2222<br />\n社會福利署：2343 2255<br />\n明愛向晴軒：18288<br />\n<br />\n年輕人專線<br />\n香港輔導及心理學會：WhatsApp熱線6218 1084 (提供英語及粵語專業輔導服務)<br />\n生命熱線：青少年生命專線 2382 0777<br />\n賽馬會青少年網上輔導平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"https://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=ad4e49b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191230/s00001/1577682873267/%E5%9F%8E%E9%96%80%E6%B0%B4%E5%A1%98%E7%8F%BE%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191230%2Fs00001%2F1577682873267%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A1%2598%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E5%25B1%258D&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=a0b63468\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191230%2Fs00001%2F1577682873267%2F%25E5%259F%258E%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25A1%2598%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2594%25B7